Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:56.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Upper Yard" "Angel Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess there's nothing\Nyou can do, hanging there like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is that important to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamakiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just thought I'd start hauling\Nthe wood for the ship's repairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You planning to swim across?\N--Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those big sharks are in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! This is how Jaya looked 400 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa! It's a skull!\N--It looks like a skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamakiri... Your wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right-- now is the time\Nto take down Upper Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Satori gone, we put up a\Ngood fight during today's battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's attack again tomorrow, Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter God Eneru!! Farewell to the Survivors"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Zoro! Just for a second...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not goin' with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a whiner! If you're scared,\Nthen hold it until morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would if I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go pee by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold-hearted, Zoro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be anyone with the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to see through all this fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He goes to take a piss, then falls\Nasleep out here. He's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Ghost... G-G-Ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit dreamin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost! A ghost...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be hard to talk while\Nyou're biting your lower lip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, Eneru-sama summoned\Nus because you let Wyper go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to get worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However much they struggle,\Nmere Shandians cannot escape us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such is their fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing but an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had Eneru-sama left it all\Nto me from the very start,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything would have\Nbeen taken care of today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his mood wouldn't have been spoiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:07:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gedatsu. It would be\Nimpossible for a fool like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll warn you two now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or else you'll lose control of your\NMantra and end up just like Satori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who needs\Nto know his place, Ohm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't start acting haughty just\N'cause you beat ol' Gan Fall, Shura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God. The priests have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! You're so hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! It's only because\Nthese guys drag me down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I can't use my powers to their fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would fare much better if you let\Nme handle the entire island alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some mighty big talk there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you just how "skilled" you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the sorrowful path of\Nenlightenment... The Iron Ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your worthless ordeal is nothing but pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My swamp is the supreme ordeal!\NWant to give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gedatsu-sama. That must be tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To cross your arms, you need to\Nput your hands under your elbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How careless of me!\N--Come! That is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are in God's presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presence? I don't see him anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he called us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Eneru-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train some more. You're all too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you don't wish to wind\Nup as pathetic as Satori did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called us here just to tell us that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to have taken much\Nnotice of those Blue Sea people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru-sama. If you're referring to Satori...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was simply too inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his lousy "Ball Ordeal" and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, you're weak, Shura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gan Fall is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! I finished him off myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not in tip-top shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he seems to be friends with the\NBlue Sea people for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a stubborn old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are the Blue Sea people after?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their aim is gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do they know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island was originally part of the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not strange for Blue Sea\Npeople to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, they will make their move tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Shandians will attack again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are that you each\Nrun an area of Upper Yard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're not allowed to\Ninterfere with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, I will let you enter all areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can set up your ordeals wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can also ignore the rules\Nand go as wild as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've almost completed the Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's put an end to this island\Nand set forth for the world of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that these people defeated Satori...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've made themselves\Ncomplete enemies of Eneru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Shandians won't\Noverlook this chance, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Eneru... Just what is it you desire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did put up a good fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we will break into God's shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Eneru will be--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! It's just like I said! Someone was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry's been repaired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it! It wasn't a dream, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mast was completely\Nsnapped off, but now it's all fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just standing this heavy thing\Nup must be hard work by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I hate to say it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are nice people out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone here! I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who'd fix our ship for us out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only people besides us in\NUpper Yard are our enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not the flying model anymore, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's got me wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the person know what\Nthe Merry originally looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd they know it didn't have\Na crest or wings or a tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you see, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really sounds like it could\Nonly happen in a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you loafing around for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have lots to do, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not curious, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About who fixed the Going Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if someone wrecked it, but\Nsince it's fixed, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you wanna find the\Nperson and thank them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Merry. Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Watch as I, President of\Nthe Lowering-the-Merry Company,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,use my greatness to get the ship off the altar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Vice President of the\NLowering-the-Merry Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being relied on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you planning to do, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! You're awesome, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't really work, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:17:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured this might happen,\Nso I devised a secret backup plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are huge skysharks here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are! Swarms of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a way we can utilize their power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The skysharks' power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They got lots of power!\NI can guarantee that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Chopper... I got a little job for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you say! I'm being relied on!\NI'll do anything at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Usopp! Don't tell me I'm being used as...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry skysharks are gonna try to bite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No bait! I don't wanna be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, skyshark!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurray! We did it!\N--Way to go, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piece o' cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. Here's the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The search team will go\Nthis way, straight south...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "right eye" should\Nhave some sort of ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so watch out for enemies\Nand bring some gold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to investigate the ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You keep talking about\Nthe gold, but you're not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want the gold, but without any danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so weird, Nami! Weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, we'll leave the island in the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be in danger, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head for the beach ruins\Narea as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet up there, and then\Nescape from this sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be super-rich pirates!\NWe can buy whatever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! I can eat all the meat I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape, huh? Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's nice weather today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are above the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's meet safely on the eastern shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright!\N--Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be the Shandians who are\Nwelcomed by my String Ordeal,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the Blue Sea people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect weather for\Nthe festival about to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're far apart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That on those days when\Nyou're brought to tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a friend here to share the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That far-off feeling we refuse to concede
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it just be a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eternal brilliance that\Neveryone is searching for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will surely embrace it with our own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's set out for the gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you! Once we get\Nthe gold, we'll be rich pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things're finally getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring God and the guerrillas\Nand everything else on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel reassured with you guys around!\NAll right! I'll try hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Giant Snake Bares Its Fangs!\NThe Survival Game Begins"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
